      <section eId="sec_15_7_40">
        <num>15-7-40</num>
        <content>
          <p>The courts governed by this chapter shall be deemed always open for the disposition of matters properly cognizable by them; however, all trials on the merits shall be conducted at trial terms regularly prescribed by local laws, as now or hereafter amended, creating the individual courts.</p>
